{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef22536bba","title":"在《人民日报》发表《关于胡风反党集团的第二批材料》的编者按语稿中加写的两段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a17c38173e","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"ef22536bba"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c6578eceee","type":"title","text":"在《人民日报》发表《关于胡风反党集团的第二批材料》的编者接语稿中加写的两段话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"ef22536bba"},{"id":"35f7d66b3a","type":"paragraph","text":"有些同情胡风或者口头上反对胡风但内心是同情胡风的人们在说，那些材料大都是解放以前的，不能据此定罪。那末，好吧，现在请看第二批材料。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"ef22536bba"},{"id":"9ac187a983","type":"paragraph","text":"反革命的胡风分子同其他公开的或暗藏的反革命分子一样，他们是把希望寄托在反革命政权的复辟和人民革命政权的倒台的。他们认为，这就是他们要“等待”的“时机”。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"ef22536bba"}],"page":{"id":"36a438680a","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"ef22536bba","start":101,"end":101}}}},"__N_SSG":true}